7 Ic secge ðæt ðonne ðæt synfulle sawl
8 him becumeð beforan, eal hit andetteð;
9 and se synna gewita

10 gesihð hwylc helle stede hire gedafenað;
11 he swingð his tægl mid ðære swipan
12 swa oft swa fela ðara ðinga ðe he hi niðer asendan wile.

